summary: Reformer New York Pilates Exercises Increases muscle strength:
title: Reformer New York Pilates Exercises Increases muscle strength:
body: The reformer New York Pilates exercises are best for you as they give better and quick results with minimum effort. These exercises are done lying down on a sliding bed-like structure and include body movements that work the muscles while not you having to huff and puff such as you would on doing regular cardio or weight lifting exercises. The tough springs on the Reformer frame give resistance as you perform New York Pilates exercises movements, strengthening your muscles and toning your body. Unlike the more static, mat-based mostly version, in a Reformer class, you may lift, push and stretch; working deep into your muscles without a visit to the free weights area. Moreover, the springs are adjusted to supply different levels of resistance, thus you can vary your workout and constantly set yourself new strength challenges.

So here's a mix of characters and animes I admire mixed with photos and stories of my travels along with tips and gear reviews. It might not be every week, but expect Waifu Wednesdays and Gear Review Saturdays. Enjoy

summary: New report measures economic loss of youth mental illness
title: New report measures economic loss of youth mental illness
body:
A new report suggests parents who miss work to help children suffering from anxiety cost the Ontario economy $421 million a year. The report, released Wednesday by Children’s Mental Health Ontario, looked at data collected in 2017.

Read more from CTV Health News https://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/new-report-measures-economic-loss-of-youth-mental-illness-1.4286374

caption:
Cool! Roger shared his post:

I saw my nutritionist yesterday. She wants me to start writing down what I am eating and how much. Guess I could, when I was doing that I saw lots of changes quick. I was calorie counting, but carb, fat, and protein counting mostly. She said what I was doing was extreme, but it was working. However if I do it her way, it allows me to come back to it where the way I was doing it I had to do it on the spot.

summary: Iris Publishers - Online Journal of Complimentary & Alternative Medicine
title: Iris Publishers - Online Journal of Complimentary & Alternative Medicine
body:
We describe about one ingredient, Oxybenzone, is found in most sunscreens. Oxybenzone is effective against protecting sunburn but it has also been found to be a potent hormone disruptor [1]. This ingredient mimics estrogen in the bodies of humans, marine animals, and fish. This article will discuss product and ingredient recommendations to protect your health, the health of your family, and our environment, particularly, our oceans. For More Information,

https://irispublishers.com/ojcam/abstract/sunscreen-and-effects-of-oxybenzone.ID.000504.php
